name: Web3 Hackers Collective Membership NFT
description:
The owner of this NFT has a right to vote on proposals submitted to the W3HC DAO. 

The mission statement of the Web3 Hackers Collective is "We want to build integrations through mentoring and learning." 

View the DAO on Tally: https://www.tally.xyz/gov/web3-hackers-collective 

https://w3hc.org
